#teamngidol


warning before reading my userpage
too lazy to input any image, so deal with a lot of text okay ?
also hi there whoever seeing my userpage.


Facebook | Youtube Channel | Tumblr


my osu! journey
  1. 2013 : Starting play this game in 16th May 2013, and my first play beatmap on mania *i know its not mania mode beatmap, but 2013 didnt have much ranked mania map and what did you expect from newcomer player in this year ?*
    ppv1 era, and i basicly using my experience from O2Jam (Official e-games and a lot of private server but kinda long time ago) to play.
  2. 2014 : In January starting change to Midare, no, not this one. heck i even dont know who in the heck create that acc..
    in this year i experience a lot of things, like ppv1 to ppv2 (when DT = +++ pp) and to ppv3 (currently right now), being top 5 indonesian osu!mania player (until MWC), being part of Indonesian MWC 7k Player The only match Indonesian got streamed actually i was not planning to participate in that tornament, but something shit happen.
    also creating the first Osu!mania Indonesian Cup alongside with Vdc and Akebono
  3. 2015 : Request revert nickname back from Midare to projectc1 (currently right now)
    sadly in 22nd May 2015 my PC somehow broken (and still not buying new one until now) so starting less play, and skill went down
  4. 2016 : Invitation by Fiea to join once more in MWC 2016 but alas being drunk in some match like vs Italy
    even less active in this year.
  5. 2017 : planning to retired (?) or at least back to organize OMIC again when i got brand new PC/Laptop
HOS
for those who're waiting for hall of shame list, i decided not to post anymore cuz due to reasonable input from "someone"
besides, ppv4 should be less that shit right ?


Still in progress v(ilostcountalreadylol)
